divs: Sighting DetailsFour White "orbs?" of the eastern part of Redding California (dispayed a uneven triange shape between them durning part of their air display). Appeared to be White (or reflective silver) in color. They moved in a spining pattern for 2 minutes then lined up and treked slowly through the sky until reaching a simi-large cloud. After entering cloud observed for 10 more minutes, but never seen the objects exit.
